<br />
*** Announcing The Legacy of Ykesha ***<br />
<br />
The Legacy of Ykesha will be the first download-only extension for EverQuest. This product will not be available in stores. This extension will include some great new gameplay features, as well as new zones for characters ranging from level 35 up to level 60.<br />
<br />
Legacy of Ykesha Features include:<br />
<br />
A new playable race: Frogloks<br />
Enhanced Looking For Group Tool<br />
New Cartography System<br />
New Magic Item slot: Charms<br />
Armor Dyes<br />
Dozens of new creatures<br />
Expanded bank capacity<br />
New zones<br />
New spells<br />
<br />
For more information, please visit <a href=http://www.legacyofykesha.com target=_blank>www.legacyofykesha.com</a>
